        {
            "title": "特朗普白宮晤澤連斯基火藥味濃 當眾批「拿第三次世界大戰來賭博」",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/0e4bec02595e2dcaf73a9bc0b69f8729/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250301/_2025030102184145042.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\"></figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>美國總統特朗普於當地週五在白宮會晤烏克蘭總統澤連斯基，準備雙方簽署備受關注的礦產協議，惟在橢圓形辦公室會談期間，雙方發生激烈爭論，場面火藥味濃。特朗普當眾批評澤連斯基正在「拿第三次世界大戰來賭博」。\n\n</p>\n<p>這場對話在美國副總統范斯指責澤連斯基公然討論敏感問題、不尊重美國夥伴後，進一步升溫。\n\n</p>\n<p>特朗普強調烏克蘭對美國援助的依賴，表示：「你現在的處境並不好。」\n\n</p>\n<p>他還批評澤連斯基沒有對美國表達足夠的感謝，並指責他在美國進行的政治活動與華府利益相悖。\n\n</p>\n<p>這場原本旨在敲定烏克蘭重建經濟協議的會談，最終凸顯了雙方在安全保障及對俄羅斯的外交策略上存在的嚴重分歧。\n\n</p>\n<p> \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2055611/即時-國際-特朗普白宮晤澤連斯基火藥味濃-當眾批-拿第三次世界大戰來賭博",
            "pub_date": "2025-03-01 02:31:26",
            "source": "stheadline",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "深水埗的士自炒撞壆反側 司機乘客一度受困輕傷送院",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"深水埗的士自炒撞壆反側 司機乘客一度受困輕傷送院。蔡楚輝攝\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/ef5a925045097edd67d6e6e114414b97/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250301/_2025030101354863583.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">深水埗的士自炒撞壆反側 司機乘客一度受困輕傷送院。蔡楚輝攝</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>深水埗發生車禍。今日（1日）凌晨零時許，一輛載客的士沿着連翔道，由油麻地向長沙灣方向行駛期間，途至長沙灣副食品批發市場對開位置時，疑為閃避其他車輛，急扭右軚，「自炒」撞向快線石壆。\n\n</p>\n<p>的士隨即向左反側傾覆，男司機及男乘客受困。消防到場後，以鐵架支撐的士車身，並協助兩人自行爬出車廂，輕傷送院治理。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4111048/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"消防到場後，以鐵架支撐的士車身，並協助兩人自行爬出車廂。蔡楚輝攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/8b59336dd5a775477a4a7d67f1dd8785/2025-03/14.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        消防到場後，以鐵架支撐的士車身，並協助兩人自行爬出車廂。蔡楚輝攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4111049/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"現場所見，的士司機年紀較大，左邊膝蓋擦傷。蔡楚輝攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/05eec4471f6690df44df9ad2d9e1440a/2025-03/11.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        現場所見，的士司機年紀較大，左邊膝蓋擦傷。蔡楚輝攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4111050/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"男乘客同被送院治理。蔡楚輝攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d02ccb8d5d1e3cb53fdeb5c6694062ea/2025-03/13.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        男乘客同被送院治理。蔡楚輝攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4111051/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"的士反側路中。蔡楚輝攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/85cc875d84a4bd6db4f2e86fbcc61834/2025-03/16.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        的士反側路中。蔡楚輝攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4111052/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"救護員用紗布為的士司機包紮頭部。蔡楚輝攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d14c75d6a303cac3460072513ba5f487/2025-03/12.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        救護員用紗布為的士司機包紮頭部。蔡楚輝攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>現場所見，的士司機年紀較大，左邊膝蓋擦傷，救護員用紗布為他包紮頭部。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
