        {
            "title": "有片｜葵青貨櫃碼頭兩貨船相撞  多個貨櫃墮海",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<div id=\"vdo-player-container\">\n<video class=\"video-js vjs-default-skin\" controls=\"\" id=\"vdo-player\" muted=\"\" playsinline=\"\" poster=\"\" width=\"100%\">\n<source src=\"https://video.hkhl.hk/404e792ef5f171ef800487c6371c0102/a5546e20e32a4e219f861c49e7181c62-c3e42ed53c86c934932dfe3ad27f54e1-ld.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\">\n                        Your browser does not support the video tag.\n                    </source></video>\n<div class=\"vdo-ad-container web\" data-vslot=\"vod_ad\" id=\"div-gpt-vad-67c1e6777576a\"></div>\n<div class=\"vdo-ad-container mweb\" data-vslot0=\"vod_ad,2\" id=\"div-gpt-vad-67c1e6777576c\"></div>\n</div>\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/d1c0e67527849910be22ca3df74b5307/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250301/_2025030100255950490.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\"></figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>葵青貨櫃碼頭發生貨船相撞事故。根據網上流傳片段，於貨櫃碼頭近岸海面，一艘粉紅色船身的貨船攔腰撞上一艘藍色船身、載滿貨櫃的貨船，其後粉紅色貨船緩緩退開，藍色貨船上至少有3個貨櫃跌落海面，擊起水花。\n\n</p>\n<p>據報粉紅色船身貨船隸屬日本航運公司「海洋網聯船務」（Ocean Network Express，簡稱ONE）。\n\n</p>\n<p>暫時未知兩船有否船員受傷。\n\n</p>\n<p> \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2055608/即時-港聞-有片-葵青貨櫃碼頭兩貨船相撞-多個貨櫃墮海",
            "pub_date": "2025-03-01 00:41:32",
            "source": "stheadline",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
